    "id": "69ea4f7a6be32fced492fbc3",
    "name": "Iai Style",
    "description": "The art of Iai came from the Island of Kirara, a sword style utilizing Kiraran blades. The Youkai were known for their highly lethal speed and technique in preference over raw power. Iaidoka are quite rare, students of elusive Kiraran Masters who only train two students at a time.",
